Version 15, February 2012
    - more rectangle() clip workaround

Version 14, February 2012
    - clip to 0,0,width,height (rectangle() workaround for libgd2.0.36
      which is supposed to do this itself but doesn't)

Version 13, August 2011
    - fix diamond() coordinates

Version 12, July 2011
    - new -quality_percent option for JPEG
    - diamond() using polygon

Version 11, June 2011
    - new -file_format
    - load() croak on bad file contents
    - fix load()/new() trouble with filenames like GIF8.png

Version 10, February 2011
    - fix Makefile.PL for perl 5.6

Version 9, November 2010
    - help 1x1 filled ellipse on past libgd

Version 8, November 2010
    - ellipse() $fill parameter

Version 7, October 2010
    - use Image:Base 1.09 for ellipse() fixes to chain up to
    - ask for GD 2.45 for GD::Simple / GD::Group fix

Version 6, September 2010
    - test manifest only as an author test

Version 5, July 2010
    - lower a couple of stray "use 5.010"s

Version 4, July 2010
    - workaround for apparent GD bug where an unfilled y1==y2
      rectangle gets sides y-1 to y+1, outside the x1,y1 x2,y2 area

Version 3, July 2010
    - fix ellipse() positioning
    - add 4-digit hex colours too
    - add $image->new() to copy

Version 2, June 2010
    - fix badly botched xy() set pixel
    - better colour None handling
    - new add_colours()

Version 1, June 2010
    - the first version
